{"tid":792402,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨遊大阪🇯🇵］有冇巴絲9月中去 順手請教下","createTime":"2018-08-24T14:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T05:34:53.000Z","uid":30660,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a31e2bd91a8e4101cd112fff3d261220f08010af","tid":792402,"uid":30660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟第一次去日本<br />\n見機票平平地就買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  12/9-17/9<br />\n<br />\n住天王寺first cabin abeno<br />\n<br />\n點知諗行程諗左成個月都諗唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.  啲一日兩日pass 係咪只有機場買？有冇啲係必買or性價比比較高<br />\n<br />\n2. 最主要想去姬路城 本來打算plan其中一日一早起身去某個市場食啲野就過去 行完再返六甲山同有馬溫泉 但唔知會唔會太趕 ？ <br />\n<br />\n3. 京都如果安排得一日會唔會好急  如果京都只有一日時間你地會點安排？（聽講清水寺維修緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？）<br />\n<br />\n4. 係咪除左心齋橋 道頓堀係會夜啲之外 入夜就無其他地方行？過左JR時間係咪得返的士可以選擇？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲撞到時間一齊食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  12/9-17/9"},{"pid":"3a79ad3a6c96bba915909f5865d078422f62e155","tid":792402,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"機票買左幾錢？"},{"pid":"805db25ddd69eaa4f6a1c870cc0d7588c6702a16","tid":792402,"uid":30660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a79ad3a6c96bba915909f5865d078422f62e155","tid":792402,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"機票買左幾錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"連行理連稅1600"},{"pid":"9f1df6298a3396cac3988eec885265f919742093","tid":792402,"uid":65142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:31:41.000Z"